{"tid":469392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國東南部連續發生強震 首爾多地有震感","createTime":"2017-11-15T09:13:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T09:06:30.000Z","uid":37554,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"879575830a81c7ef260f9bb995cbd718da57efd5","tid":469392,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T09:13:31.000Z","msg":"韓國氣象廳稱，當地時間15日下午2點29分，在韓國慶尚北道浦項市北區6公里處，發生5.5級地震。不久，第二波規模5.4的地震隨之而來。首都首爾等地也有震感，目前無傷亡報告。<br />\n<br />\n韓聯社報導，雖然連續發生強震，但震區的核電廠未受損。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DOpzeXZX0AAoQKF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDOpzeXZX0AAoQKF.jpg&h=b0106bce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DOqAqJgWkAAbwos.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDOqAqJgWkAAbwos.jpg&h=f32e806f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a0f66496ae807428c60647f3ecf613f1bd2a07c","tid":469392,"uid":52946,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T09:19:46.000Z","msg":"北泡核試姐 無事既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce4136336e18ad78f16d26d565a4f3e2334d070","tid":469392,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T09:36:41.000Z","msg":"南韓媒體報導，此次震災造成了LG旗下所屬的顯示器部份生產線也停機。"},{"pid":"7f45c99dc65acfc2eb780c3d2878e411e7d29e77","tid":469392,"uid":38255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T09:38:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/143928_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F143928_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=073c3458&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n平成29年11月15日14時37分 気象庁発表<br />\n15日14時29分頃地震がありました。<br />\n震源地は<span style=\"color: red;\">朝鮮半島南部</span>（北緯36.1度、東経129.5度）で、<br />\n震源の深さは約10km、地震の規模（マグニチュード）は<span style=\"color: red;\">5.5</span>と推定されます。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/143952_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F143952_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=f0541d5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南韓媒體報導，此次震災造成了LG旗下所屬的顯示器部份生產線也停機。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/150648_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F150648_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f2386070&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/150656_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F150656_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=639b1197&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/150701_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F150701_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9931835d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/150707_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F150707_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=84d3ea58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/150712_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F150712_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=db41b011&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n南韓最大既斷層：梁山斷層<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/153043_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F153043_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0b683323&s={SIZE}\" />[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n根據韓國的歷史書記載，其中一次發生於韓國的最強地震 (7級) ，是發生於公元 779 年的新羅時代，當時的地震發生於韓國的慶州市內。<br />\n<br />\n月城原子力發電所（韓語：월성원자력발전소）位於大韓民國慶尚北道慶州市的一座核能發電廠。"},{"pid":"509cd494a24152f06426605d28b9c8ff046da25c","tid":469392,"uid":14103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T09:57:13.000Z","msg":"好少聽到韓國地震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50bcafc011f8b5dbfb78ca0ff98abb096d431f22","tid":469392,"uid":38255,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T10:09:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好少聽到韓國地震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n韓國人幾年前都唔覺地震關自己事，<br />\n係近年東南部梁山斷層突然好似蘇醒返咁，上年都有次5.8係浦項南面既慶州，<br />\n亦即係古書記載7級地震既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n近幾年活躍左既原因有兩個可能：<br />\n<br />\n一、311地震直接影響附近板塊，令梁山斷層蘇醒<br />\n二、北泡多次核試既人工地震激發左梁山斷層<br />\n三、以上兩者加埋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec752a944c420f5d2b6379a0ebfe23735ddd63e","tid":469392,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T10:10:21.000Z","msg":"小9事"},{"pid":"e1dacdf5e5641ff60cadeacb368a4be0bd01b03a","tid":469392,"uid":58359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T10:10:44.000Z","msg":"以為金仔又射野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d6798d3ed0990740ca7f3c53cb9d3852b7941f3","tid":469392,"uid":45368,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T10:11:08.000Z","msg":"垃圾韓國<br />\n比著香港一定無事"},{"pid":"31634735748b4d95d31828c38df7723b4149778c","tid":469392,"uid":4713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T10:11:24.000Z","msg":"D day<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a9cae6c34e46c362bba2ce6f82046db39e8e79","tid":469392,"uid":38255,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T10:39:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾韓國<br />\n比著香港一定無事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港5.5既話，馬頭圍土瓜灣果堆樓隨時冧一成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8872bcb015f63f42fd310bc8c3f420c991a7f842","tid":469392,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T10:47:01.000Z","msg":"其實韓國真係好落後<br />\n5.5級已經搞成咁<br />\n利申韓狗"},{"pid":"961a42545378eb402eab6f202b14f45afeb87708","tid":469392,"uid":41375,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T10:58:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>垃圾韓國<br />\n比著香港一定無事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港5.5既話，馬頭圍土瓜灣果堆樓隨時冧一成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n深水埗唔知會死幾多人"},{"pid":"779e5e104431341b70d3690a92b65f36a3ff9583","tid":469392,"uid":11148,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:05:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>垃圾韓國<br />\n比著香港一定無事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港5.5既話，馬頭圍土瓜灣果堆樓隨時冧一成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n深水埗唔知會死幾多人</blockquote><br />\n香港如果真係有7級地震,死既人數應該上百萬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a02cecd639c370a038c815e46f9a7d34cb5672","tid":469392,"uid":45368,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T12:57:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>垃圾韓國<br />\n比著香港一定無事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港5.5既話，馬頭圍土瓜灣果堆樓隨時冧一成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n深水埗唔知會死幾多人</blockquote><br />\n香港如果真係有7級地震,死既人數應該上百萬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你老母踩港撚<br />\n香港基建世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cd2237e14b441c7c4a808d26b45d4c8ab7d9c19","tid":469392,"uid":38255,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T13:03:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>垃圾韓國<br />\n比著香港一定無事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港5.5既話，馬頭圍土瓜灣果堆樓隨時冧一成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n深水埗唔知會死幾多人</blockquote><br />\n香港如果真係有7級地震,死既人數應該上百萬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港境內發生7級地震機會應該無，<br />\n東部最盡5.5級，西部最盡6級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港附近其實都有斷層，不過大部份都好零碎，主要有3條較長較大機會引發5級以上地震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但3條斷層暫時全部都認為處於休眠狀態（唔似韓國梁山斷層咁認為已經重新活躍）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n東面有1條由大亞灣延伸至九龍北部，認為最盡5級地震但保險會以5.5級封頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n西面有1條由大嶼山一路經路環橫琴島延伸到上川島，認為最盡可以有6級地震，<br />\n1905年珠海對出海面發生過5.5級地震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n南面海域有1條由擔捍群島延伸到汕頭一帶，末端接上主斷裂帶台灣地震震帶，呢到認為有能力觸發7級地震，1918年汕頭南澳島就發生過7級地震，香港距離300公里亦有建築物損毀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 若果同一條斷層係南端既擔捍群島爆發7級地震，距離只有幾十公里既香港影響應該唔細。<br />\n<br />\n不過3條斷層都處於休眠狀態，上面講既係佢潛在爆到幾級地震，實際真出事既機會極細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔使杞人憂天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要擔心的話擔心海嘯好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n即使擔捍群島海域7級大地震，由於唔係板塊邊緣係觸發唔到大海嘯（1米內既高度都有d機會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）。香港要擔心既海嘯威脅係台灣西岸至菲律賓西岸既潛沒帶，有能力觸發8級以上大地震，真係發生咁強既地震，包括香港在內廣東沿岸最高可能有8米海嘯，大亞灣嶺澳核電廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/210158_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F210158_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3e9a2578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然機率都好低，但呢條係活生生既板塊邊緣，一直都被世界認定係隨時會大地震既位置黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bf99498ae9c4c064d9b9bfd152f421a5321ba38","tid":469392,"uid":5253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T13:07:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>垃圾韓國<br />\n比著香港一定無事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港5.5既話，馬頭圍土瓜灣果堆樓隨時冧一成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n深水埗唔知會死幾多人</blockquote><br />\n香港如果真係有7級地震,死既人數應該上百萬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港境內發生7級地震機會應該無，<br />\n東部最盡5.5級，西部最盡6級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然機率都好低，但呢條係活生生既板塊邊緣，一直都被世界認定係隨時會大地震既位置黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bdc7f22a5a3154557bc7a7946cace1d297f2e38","tid":469392,"uid":61359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T13:07:15.000Z","msg":"香港D樓好似無防震,一震D幾十層既樓係咪會一排過冧哂"},{"pid":"9bbe6aac5be4ae665a5e476ca16c4ff996ad8526","tid":469392,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T13:09:53.000Z","msg":"震到成地眼耳口鼻，執都有排執"},{"pid":"ac22b89f7ce7839cb4194242d4b62d845049d53e","tid":469392,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T13:14:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b89c7d3839604900aa940c1cb70d337bfc552cf","tid":469392,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T13:15:54.000Z","msg":"講返正題<br />\n<br />\n南韓5.4地震全國有感史上第二強震已致39傷2傷勢嚴重<br />\n<br />\n上年5.8都係8輕傷，應該關浦項人口較多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f6d81172e00d513cc33ee6bc2e6ec29f1c37e5d","tid":469392,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T13:16:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5b175bf6f49aa57de43cf6666422f6f812aa32","tid":469392,"uid":38255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T13:17:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港D樓好似無防震,一震D幾十層既樓係咪會一排過冧哂</blockquote><br />\n好多高樓都有抗震技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港既抗震係抗風附加，可以抵禦地震水平搖動，但地震仲包括垂直震動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5828e96bac6f1629697a9f739a6c094b0aff0a02","tid":469392,"uid":27147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T14:38:54.000Z","msg":"咁岩喺浦項。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為餘震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今晚訓唔訓得成都係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f61cea585e2a0f21e36f8df3df080ad0e8836b","tid":469392,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:03:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁岩喺浦項。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為餘震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今晚訓唔訓得成都係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去日本玩遇到地震叫預左，<br />\n去韓國玩遇到地震仲要咁強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}